Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.45,0:40:03.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fnGoodfish\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}The cicadas laugh out in song
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.28,0:40:10.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}to the red evening sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}The way back home is long
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:24.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}but I promised to come here again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.16,0:40:40.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}The summer is in full bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.74,0:40:54.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}making you look more beautiful than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.48,0:41:15.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}I thought the tale would never end
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.77,0:41:22.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}but I realize now that something comes after
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.27,0:41:30.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}The crows too took flight
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.04,0:41:38.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}and went somewhere far, far away
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.73,0:41:54.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}The summer flies by
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.84,0:42:08.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}to hide away its treasures till next year
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.65,0:43:03.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}I'll never ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.37,0:43:10.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}those golden summer days
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.24,0:43:18.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}That summer which brought joy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.41,0:43:25.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}to my boring everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.39,0:43:44.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}And look! Summer is here again
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.31,0:43:57.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}to help me keep my promise of that day
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.82,0:44:11.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}The summer is still in bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.59,0:44:25.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,300)\blur3.97}making you look more beautiful than ever
